{"tid":2084363,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"香港最後一首獨立改歌","createTime":"2020-06-29T08:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T06:00:59.000Z","uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0b11b87997f4da9025189ca1c9db16473448c2","tid":2084363,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這原是一首本土樂隊送給黑人種族的歌曲，<br />\n但現在是我們的了！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">改自 : <ins><strong>Beyond - Amani</ins></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香 港的生活爭鬥<br />\nBlack Bloc準備足夠<br />\n穿梭街道只想覓自由<br />\n不 不需得到不反<br />\n香港國會知道<br />\n香港口號遍佈這地球<br />\n無力與終結的覺醒<br />\n流汗喊口號帶悲憤<br />\n在控訴抗爭到最後<br />\n傷痛是手足<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唯有向世界呼叫<br />\nHONG～ KONG～ <br />\nINDEPENDENCE！ <br />\nINDEPENDENCE～ <br />\nWE WIN！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n權利與擁有的理想<br />\n愚昧與偏見黨安法<br />\n若這裡抗爭到最後<br />\n不會是和平<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我向世界呼叫<br />\nHONG～ KONG～ <br />\nINDEPENDENCE！ <br />\nINDEPENDENCE～ <br />\nWE WIN！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span>"},{"pid":"44cd2fb90e56ebe94d1df76646606339801502f6","tid":2084363,"uid":235316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Facebook Instagram airdrop都要post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n可以一齊轉埋Icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f